    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions factor is acknowledged; the assessment team determined that the overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission claim given the controlled nature of ASTM F1717 testing and the consistency of results across three independent FEA codes and two laboratories.",
